{
  "stem": "17135.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 348.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had heavily armored cars, you know, not tanks, but-- but heavy armored cars.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the SS panicked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were scared of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were afraid for their own lives, and they gave orders.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] were three or four big trains with-- with hundreds of cattle cars to stop loading and whoever is loaded go, because they were afraid that they will come.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And those idiots-- if they would have done that, the SS would have fled.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If the armored patrol had permission to-- to come close to the railway station, they could have saved tens of thousands of prisoners.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But they didn't, either out of stupidity, or-- or because of orders they had not to make contact.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the rest were not loaded-- about 15,000.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We have to march.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's the famous death march.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This 15,000 column marched for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] eight weeks, or nine weeks, and it was the worst thing that I've ever seen in my life.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It-- all the horrors that I've been through in Auschwitz in-- in the years and Sachsenhausen, is no comparison to what we suffered on the death march.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The guards-- now listen to this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Guess who the guards were?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You must have heard that the Grand Mufti of Jerusalem was invited by Hitler.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The British wanted to arrest him, because he started the riots in '36 in-- in Palestine, and they reported him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Hitler invited him, and he was sitting in Berlin throughout of war like a favorite guest in a palace.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had all the luxury.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in return for the favors of Hitler, he organized two Muslim brigades from Bosnia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Are you listening?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From Bosnia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and they were in the SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were all young men, I would say, from 18 to 24.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
